Midterm Exam
Feb 19, 2026 9:12 AM
The midterm exam will take place next week: Tuesday, Feb. 24th from 2-4pm (2 hours).

The exam is delivered on paper - you cannot use any electronic devices during the exam. However, it is fully open book - you can bring as many printouts, cheatsheets and paper notes as you want.

During the exam, you will have to:

answer multiple choice questions
provide (short) written answers to questions
implement a very simple API
fill the blanks in an OpenAPI YAML file
write basic Python code for the API endpoints (app.py)
The exam will cover all topics (lectures and labs) that you have been working on in weeks 1 to 7.

